Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:21.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披天马圣衣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天际 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无迟疑的双眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛着泪光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:37.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不含一丝阴翳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使身死战地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:47.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了跨越那障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们坚定不移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如星辰般闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.94,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星座起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作指引胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的双翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让那有限的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧不息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们至深的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.04,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未知的极限的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.26,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情编织成的神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:16.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界已经失去了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都归功于萨图恩大人的伟大力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里却还有人妄图抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.18,0:02:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是纠缠不休的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是从你们身上夺走时间与圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.59,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经远远无法满足我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须连你们的命也搭上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有帕拉斯与雅典娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位女神的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们这两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真敢口出狂言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会放任这种事情发生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界失去的时间 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我们来取回
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我们一定会打倒萨图恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够感觉到 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.05,0:03:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.11,0:03:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.50,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越神明！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.95,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被迷惑了 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.62,0:03:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙已经不是昴了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是萨图恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要操之过急
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.77,0:03:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人忌惮的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.48,0:03:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.61,0:04:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭这种程度的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.83,0:04:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就想违抗神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由余亲手了结你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.01,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是黄金圣斗士 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就只有这种程度而已吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.67,0:04:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 萨图恩的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然 碰不到他一根手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无比强大的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然连星矢都被一击就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.25,0:05:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中创造了宇宙的Ω的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是站起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.76,0:05:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一路和我并肩作战的你 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是绝对不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.72,0:05:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论失败多少次 人类都会重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的话就快醒醒吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.58,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且 之后会再犯下同样的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣剑它…这增强的小宇宙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是对Ω之力产生了反应吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我了结你的性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不让这令人敬畏的Ω之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次觉醒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.39,0:06:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用这圣剑的力量 结果了你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.57,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区区人类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是无法与觉醒了的萨图恩大人抗衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.60,0:06:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可说不准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真让人火大呢 你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.64,0:07:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有必要为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将被萨图恩大人打倒的伙伴悲伤了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 你小子会死在他们前头嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你只有速度算是不落人后啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白鸟座冰河
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们真以为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打倒时刻之神萨图恩大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 若是像她们那种柔弱的神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.01,0:07:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定真能实现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能取得她们的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也就加入到弑神的行列中去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的实力不相上下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去是无法决出胜负的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.35,0:08:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭斩痕（Destructive Slash）！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极排斥（Ultimate Rejection）！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬的犹豫就会丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的圣斗士也不过如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真让人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同Ω的力量一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天马座！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙星矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨图恩 你的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次站起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.90,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来打倒！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们全都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.41,0:09:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你心中的拳已经钝化了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中的拳？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在萨图恩的身上看到了昴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是萨图恩 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雅典娜的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用这Ω的小宇宙打倒他！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才说你们做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:10:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω本身是从拯救昴的心意中萌生的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.09,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够觉醒究极中的究极小宇宙Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以说明你们对昴有多么重视
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因而 这也是无法简单舍弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的没错吧 光牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不会再踌躇 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不会再犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.49,0:10:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要拯救沙织小姐和世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就凭软弱无能的人类吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁 都无法打倒身为神明的余
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.13,0:11:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢、超越神明！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.44,0:11:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将小宇宙攻破了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是曾反抗过无数神明的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.52,0:11:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究是一介凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没结束 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.79,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨图恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星…星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早该说过了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的对手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.97,0:12:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该弑神了 弑神了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星云气流
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.08,0:13:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说我身陷你的小宇宙漩涡之中 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.13,0:13:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动弹不得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.48,0:13:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再见到无谓的流血了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 欧罗巴 你可得给力点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.13,0:14:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 雅典娜和帕拉斯就交给哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腿 腿冻结了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对零度 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零下273度的冻气已经封住了你的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.98,0:14:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你小子就是为了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才故意吃下我的攻击的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.46,0:14:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就无法施展你引以为傲的速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.06,0:14:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受了究极排斥的一击 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子为何还能毫发无损
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打中你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你出招的那一刻 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就已经将你的拳头冻结了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻衣…竟然！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.90,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以摧毁圣衣为乐的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:15:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今眼见自己的刻衣被毁坏 感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钻石星尘！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.47,0:15:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥怎会在区区圣斗士面前 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,败下阵来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才的那番话 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.41,0:15:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原封不动地还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨图恩的左右手也不过如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人失望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 米拉先生 你已经跪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没办法 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.04,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我一个人来终结这一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 欧罗巴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和传闻中的一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到星云气流竟能有这样的威力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 我是不会收手的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨图恩大人的世界很快就要实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我岂能在这种地方退却
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.47,0:16:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星云风暴！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多…多么强大的小宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是 星云…风…暴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你已经筋疲力尽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经预料到你会使出星云风暴了 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座的瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.74,0:17:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该继续弑神之路了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 伤似乎比想象的要严重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.53,0:17:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取下失去意识的雅典娜和帕拉斯的人头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是轻而易举…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆敢…将帕拉斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么强大的小宇宙 你是从哪里得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使付出生命 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要保护帕拉斯大人到底！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纵使燃尽全部小宇宙 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耗尽生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要打倒你！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下 泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢欺骗帕拉斯大人 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧罗巴！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 我有个好建议
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.03,0:17:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分给帕拉斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 分给帕拉斯大人 一半世界如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.36,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会向萨图恩大人进言的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 泰坦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混账的鬼话 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经听腻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨星终结！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然也要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力竭了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ω的圣斗士们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.06,0:19:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手吧 已经够了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不得不战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙织小姐 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了世人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.29,0:19:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与深爱的人进行了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.80,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才终有一刻 必须亲手将一切终结啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是珍视之人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误入歧途时 就必须将其打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是珍视之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.34,0:19:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必须将其阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其打倒之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.80,0:19:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实会背负起沉痛的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.03,0:20:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士的战斗啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾俄洛斯 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.55,0:20:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你那里继承的射手座圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得这么破烂不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的圣衣啊 只要一击便好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到放出那一击为止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借给我力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那被称作圣斗士的宿命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微不足道的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.86,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.02,0:21:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中可以弑神的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄金的短剑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等这一刻好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始 目标就是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢了 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.50,0:21:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射手座的圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了你 我才能放出…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一击！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨图恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚回宇宙的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最深处吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可替代的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.86,0:22:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了夺回这些
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.88,0:22:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍摩 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.77,0:22:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.60,0:22:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.44,0:22:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊甸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.94,0:22:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们燃烧至顶点的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.40,0:22:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的战斗！ 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧、Ω的圣斗士！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:23:08.94,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星矢与萨图恩的命运是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:23:08.94,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙与同伴们，最后的战斗！！
